=Contextual Quote=

This page is inspired by the question/proposal of Pascal Desfarges:

"Question: peux-ton imaginer la notion de "communs d'urgence" ? , appropriation de bien privés pour des urgences publiques: manuels scolaires, masques, respirateurs etc. C'est communs seraient en ouverture temporaires dans des situations de crise. quelle serait la liste des "communs d'urgence" fondamentaux." (fb march 2020)


=Description=

Emergency commons are resources that are freed voluntarily and at least temporarily for helping with collaborative responses to the Corona (Covid 19) crisis and the lifestyle adaptations required by social distancing requirements (telework, remote education, etc...)



